org.locationtech.geowave.mapreduce.splits

Class GeoWaveRecordReader<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.hadoop.mapreduce.RecordReader<GeoWaveInputKey,T>
      • org.locationtech.geowave.mapreduce.splits.GeoWaveRecordReader<T>
  • Type Parameters:
    T - The native type for the reader
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    Closeable, AutoCloseable

    public class GeoWaveRecordReader<T>
extends org.apache.hadoop.mapreduce.RecordReader<GeoWaveInputKey,T>
    This class is used by the GeoWaveInputFormat to read data from a GeoWave data store.
